    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
春の弥生の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">夜</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">仄</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほの</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">天地</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あめつち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ひくゝ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">垂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">た</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れあひて、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">情</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">なさけ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のにほひいちめんに<lb />
おぼろおぼろの花ぐもり、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">精舎</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しやうじや</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の壁の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">地獄絵</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぢごくゑ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">温</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぬる</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">霞</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かすみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">纏</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ふらむ。<lb />
<lb />
森の木立の月かげを<lb />
避けて、まぶかき<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">黒鉄</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くろがね</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">甲</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かぶと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、なほも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">色白</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いろじろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">面</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おもて</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">凛々</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">りゝ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しく、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">瑠璃青</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">るりあを</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">瞳</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひとみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>きよげに、花ぐさを<lb />
わけつゝしのぶ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">騎士</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ひとり。<lb />
<lb />
『たそがれがたの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">戦闘</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たゝかひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
十騎の敵を殺したれ、<lb />
胸にさしたる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">紅薔薇</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">べにさうび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
二<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">輪</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">りん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">色</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">いろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">濃</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>くちりもせず、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">西</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">にし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">丘</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なる陣<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">指</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>すと、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">悠</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゆう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に見かへる敵の城。<lb />
<lb />
時しもあれや、矢は一つ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">空鳴</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">そらな</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>りしつつ、ひとばかり、<lb />
鎧の袖に触れて落つ。<lb />
赤き塗り矢の根のかたに<lb />
如何なる人のざれわざぞ、<lb />
にくき文こそ結びたれ。<lb />
<lb />
『<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">貪</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">むさぼ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>るものにこの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">穢土</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ゑど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<lb />
あはれみ給へ、将軍よ、<lb />
少女が胸のなさけには<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">国土</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こくど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">山河</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さんが</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も何ならむ。』<lb />
とばかり読むも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">短檠</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たんけい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
火かげまばゆくおぼえしか。<lb />
<lb />
まだ我が知らぬ酔ひごこち、<lb />
こは夢かとて立ちよれば、<lb />
壁に懸けたる我が盾に、<lb />
うつれる影は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">怨敵</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">をんてき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
かなたの王の一の姫<lb />
乱れし髪の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb"><span facs="../../../gaiji/1-91/1-91-26.png" rend="gaiji" rendition="img" source="※(「藹」の「言」に代えて「月」、第3水準1-91-26)" /></span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">らふ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>たしや。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">癡</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>け<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">果</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">は</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>てじと投げぬれば<lb />
盾は音して砕けたり。<lb />
第二の盾を手にとりて<lb />
見ればここにも不思議さよ、<lb />
うつれる姫は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">浮足</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うけあし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<lb />
わが前にしも身を投げて<lb />
よゝとばかりに縋り泣く。<lb />
<lb />
『あゝよし、さらば<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">天地</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あめつち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">有情</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うじやう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">温</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ぬる</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>みの春の夜の<lb />
花のくもりに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">溶</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">と</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>け去りて<lb />
一如無相の海となれ、<lb />
愛の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">御龕</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みづし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、姫が<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">手</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">て</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、<lb />
いまぞ楽しき罪を得む。』<lb />
<lb />
城の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">濠</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">切崖</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きりぎし</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も<lb />
夢の心地にくゞり来て、<lb />
瞳すかせば、木がくれに<lb />
さやさやとなる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">衣摺</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きぬずれ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>や、<lb />
姫は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">荒磯</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ありそ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のこほろぎの<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">藻</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">も</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>によるごとくすがりけり。<lb />
<lb />
花の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">木</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">間</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にうぐひすは<lb />
夢の世をしも歌ひたり。<lb />
蜜の如くにやはらかき<lb />
うまし<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">二人</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ふたり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のくちづけよ、<lb />
あゝ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">怨敵</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">をんてき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>と怨敵は<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">天</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>と歴史を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">無</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>みしつる。<lb />
<lb />
『青史の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">帙</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ちつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">御座</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">みくら</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>する<lb />
神もいまさば、などてこの<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">戦闘</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たゝかひ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>あらぬ初めより、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">怨恨</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うらみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をむすぶ敵軍に、<lb />
かゝるくしびの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">力</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ちから</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>もつ<lb />
姫ありとしも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">告</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>げざりし。』<lb />
<lb />
『みゆるしたまへ、父の王、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">汝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>がいとし子の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">魂</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の花<lb />
咲きくゆりぬる功徳のゆゑ、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">明日</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あす</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>より<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">後</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">のち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>のたゝかひに<lb />
王が<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">馬蹄</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ばてい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は十<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">国</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">土</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">つち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">隈</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>なく<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">印</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">しる</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しなむ。』<lb />
<lb />
『王よ與へむ、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">天</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あめ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">下</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">した</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">汝</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>が<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">利心</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とごゝろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">飽</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>くまゝに、<lb />
血汐に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">餓</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">う</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>うる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">戈</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ほこ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さきを、<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">十国</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">とくに</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の城に、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">百国</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">もゝくに</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">民</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">頭</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かうべ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に、柔らかう<lb />
口づけさせて、取り<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">統</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">す</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>べよ。』<lb />
<lb />
『国の王者にあらずとも、<lb />
かゝる<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">雄々</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">をゝ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>しき恋人は<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">真</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まこと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の人ぞ、あゝ今は<lb />
われも<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">真</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">まこと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の人の妻。』<lb />
二人をめぐるそよ風は<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">百千</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">もつち</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の花の香を吹きぬ。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
